name: Zutano unisex-baby Cozie Fleece Baby Booties With Grippers
product_description: At Zutano, we are parents first, so we understand how important it is for your baby to be comfortable, safe, and adorable in all their clothes and accessories. Quality fabric and intuitive design are our hallmarks, and we believe that’s what distinguishes our products from the rest of the must-have newborn essentials on the market. Our Cozie Fleece Baby Booties with Grippers are made with a high-quality blend of 70% cotton and polyester and are fully lined with 100% organic cotton to protect your baby’s delicate skin and keep them warm. The innovative double-snap design with gentle elastic saves you time and money and maintains your sanity by making it nearly impossible for your baby to remove our booties from their feet. No more lost socks or booties, no matter how active your little one is! Our fleece baby gripper booties are the perfect winter accessories to add to any baby registry, especially for new parents worried about safer first steps for their child. These booties for babies are long-lasting, durable, comfortable, and cute. They will become a family treasure that can be passed down from child to child or donated in good, clean condition to benefit another family. In 1989, Zutano was founded by new parents Michael and Uli Belenky, who desired a wide selection of high-quality baby clothing for their infant daughter. Designed by Uli and hand delivered by Michael on his bicycle, Zutano products found their way into Manhattan boutiques and eventually into the hearts of parents everywhere. In its over 30 years in business, Zutano has become one of the best-known US apparel and accessory brands for children. We owe much of our success to our amazing customers, who spread the word of our dedication to quality and functionality in each of our unique products. Whether you collect our rainbow of colors or receive well-loved hand-me-downs, we hope our baby clothing and accessories make your day a bit less hectic.
